* Field constants used when accessing field information for relative * datetime strings in FormattedValue. *

* There is no public constructor to this class; the only instances are the * constants defined here. *

* @hide Only a subset of ICU is exposed in Android

variables.name: LITERAL
variables.comment: * Represents a literal text string, like "tomorrow" or "days ago".

variables.name: NUMERIC
variables.comment: * Represents a number quantity, like "3" in "3 days ago".
